
The standard library {\tt threadkit\_os\_glue} package implements 
the interface to an OS specific module that glues the various 
OS-specific scheduling operations together (i.e., timeouts, I/O, signals, etc).

The {\tt threadkit\_os\_glue} package implements the \ahrefloc{api:Threadkit\_Os\_Glue}{Threadkit\_Os\_Glue} api.

The {\tt threadkit\_os\_glue} package source code is in \ahrefloc{src/lib/src/lib/thread-kit/src/posix/unix-threadkit-os-glue.pkg}{ad-kit/src/posix/threadkit-os-glue.pkg}.
